
<div class="jumbotron image-header" >
  <div class="container col-md-8">
    <h1>Meet other students that share your clubs</h1>
    <p>This is a template for a simple marketing or informational website. It includes a large callout called a jumbotron and three supporting pieces of content. Use it as a starting point to create something more unique.</p>

    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <%= link_to profile_user_path(current_user), class: "btn btn-warning btn-lg" do %>
        START CONNECTING HERE <span class="fa fa-long-arrow-right"></span>
      <% end %>
